{"tid":1314314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大圍站有人派緊‘看中國’海報，有無人知係乜野？","createTime":"2019-07-14T06:19:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T06:34:11.000Z","uid":238595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d46743559d76ebcd0e192f361e58276c1301980","tid":1314314,"uid":238595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:19:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ymcy9z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ymcy9z.jpg&h=f15e05ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0c95a44177bd5d221500f94e59a54c36e00a638","tid":1314314,"uid":24050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"ce4d76e8dd8332db7ed18b8b113bc91dda0d4a35","tid":1314314,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:29:56.000Z","msg":"7.7已經派緊，對鄰國文宣嚟"},{"pid":"8845e529b58fc89dc3e924c09c6defab72874491","tid":1314314,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"大紀元黎"},{"pid":"a12b16d68afc206ed2982249b1044a4755a0ded4","tid":1314314,"uid":24534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:33:48.000Z","msg":"《看中國》在其新聞的內容編排上以中國大陸為重點，經常報導中國大陸社會中下層老百姓的民生狀況以及官場百態，同時有適量的國際新聞，另外也有財經、移民、時尚、文化、奇聞、娛樂等等分類新聞。<br />\n由於其獨立立場，對於中華人民共和國官員的貪腐著墨較多，其報箱曾經在2008年兩度遭到中國共產黨支持者破壞。<br />\n<br />\n儘管不時地批評中國大陸政府和新浪微博的言論審查，《看中國》的中文網站也同樣對讀者評論進行言論審查。"},{"pid":"ca410fac3146610ff6c15075228a4da04d5cd4ee","tid":1314314,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8845e529b58fc89dc3e924c09c6defab72874491","tid":1314314,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:30:27.000Z","msg":"大紀元黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:34:01.000Z","msg":"sorry自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《看中國》（Vision Times）是在美國和澳洲發行的綜合性中文週報（英語：Weekly newspaper），於2001年在美國紐約創立[1]，除了在較大城市設有付費報箱（英語：Newspaper vending machine）販售報紙[2]，在一些華人社區也有設有免費報箱供人免費取閱，並在網絡上有中文、英文、西班牙文等三種語文的新聞網站。其中文網站自述「報道最新社會焦點，從不迴避有爭議主題或妥協於政治壓力」、「推崇傳統中華文化和復興其理念，以促進中華民族發展為目標而不停努力」"},{"pid":"d0eb2acce5402f8275603cb553d2a483df8ebdca","tid":1314314,"uid":176991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:34:11.000Z","msg":"看中國 = 大紀元<br />\n<br />\n幅畫係一個走左去美國嘅中國異見畫家畫<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/daxiongart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fdaxiongart%2F&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPav1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=5c27be90\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/daxiongart/</a>"}]}